                     <msContents>
                        <summary><title type="uiform">Ólafs saga helga</title>. Remarkable for this
                            text is an interpolation from <title type="uniform"
                            >Heimskringla</title>, having a few errors in common with <ref type="ms"
                                target="AM02-045-en">Codex Frisianus</ref>: the scaldic verses
                            attributed to <name type="person" key="ThoKol001">Þormóðr
                                Kolbrúnarskáld</name> instead of Þórðr Kolbeinsson and the first
                            stanza having <q xml:lang="is">ef</q> for ept; yet closer reading shows
                            that Codex Frisianus cannot be the source of the interpolated
                            part.</summary>
                        <msItem n="1" class="kon" defective="true">
